2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper involves affine transformations, which are commonly used in computer graphics. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper's focus on camera calibration and estimation of intrinsic parameters is relevant to robotics applications. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper's use of multivariate polynomial systems and root selection techniques may be of interest to the machine learning community. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper's use of image pairs and camera calibration is relevant to multimedia applications such as image and video processing.
